Finds a backward index such that
`slice.backward(index)` is minimal(maximal).

Params:
    pred = A predicate.

See_also:
    $(LREF minIndex),
    $(LREF maxPos),
    $(LREF maxIndex),
    $(REF Slice.backward, mir,ndslice,slice).
